{"tid":2031992,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"請為明天所有手足祈禱及祝福 和勇不分 平平安安","createTime":"2020-05-23T19:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T16:02:35.000Z","uid":4322,"like":388,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"3dc9b74080fcae60998be6ffa4e334db5424106a","tid":2031992,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T19:26:07.000Z","msg":"你我都知 聽日無論如何 <br />\n一定會有人傷會有人被捕<br />\n只係唔知係你係我定佢...<br />\n<br />\n所以無論你衡量後出唔出都好 我都尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但希望你可以同我一齊為聽日既手足祈禱祝福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要祝福大家平平安安回家<br />\n因為我想係連登再見到你同佢9up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>出既你 be water </strong></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜常check哨兵 宜熟讀離場路線 <br />\n忌戀戰 忌捉鬼 忌陣地<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「五大訴求」</span></strong></span><br />\n人無事先做到世界冠軍<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>唔出既你 你都會好忙</ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇直播<br />\n捐錢<br />\n外國戰線 (twitter and reddit) <br />\n做文宣<br />\n去黃店<br />\n哨兵<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「缺一不可」</strong></span></span><br />\n和勇不分<br />\n<br />\n最後無論聽日咩結局係好係壞<br />\n最緊要唔好灰心 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>晨曦必定出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正義必定勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n因為堅持所以先有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MNNDW9O.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMNNDW9O.gif&h=1b601a5b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3P2wxH8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3P2wxH8.gif&h=1ba6a0de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGsHEn9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGsHEn9.gif&h=c21d857a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bY3zvuQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbY3zvuQ.gif&h=78152d13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62h1auQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62h1auQ.png&h=c6357f06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a200f5a9950ad6ca9cd0b5d7121d384077322e86","tid":2031992,"uid":4322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T19:26:18.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"dd069754fa15c730015603eb52112b3d8850f1ef","tid":2031992,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T19:26:52.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"9eab689494f114238a972dbe42da1ce2ac7bd672","tid":2031992,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T19:27:16.000Z","msg":"Pishhh"},{"pid":"0c2b9010280b41ab4044e29c6dff01ca8b29300d","tid":2031992,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T19:28:33.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"7d0883227290094a452b3f1e443f1a5c67908398","tid":2031992,"uid":17388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T19:28:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b95ecaa80d22192b412f34022a48c73c356f3571","tid":2031992,"uid":165534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T19:28:46.000Z","msg":"Pishhh"},{"pid":"f8711b7b4aeae37754f49a1d340238a5889e954e",